  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>
      Amal Jyothi College of Engineering (AJCE), located in Kanjirappally, Kerala, is the first engineering college in Kerala to obtain NAAC accreditation with an A grade and the first new-generation engineering college in the state to secure NBA accreditation for prime departments. The college is approved by the All India Council for Technical Education (AICTE) and affiliated with APJ Abdul Kalam Technological University.
    </p>
    <div class="image-gallery">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1504384308090-c894fdcc538d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="College Campus" />
